## Sample Data

A sampled version of the processed dataset is provided for quick testing and debugging purposes.

The sample dataset contains approximately **15% of the processed data** and preserves the same schema and feature structure as the full processed dataset.

The sample data can be used to:
- Verify data loading and preprocessing pipelines
- Test feature engineering steps
- Run model training workflows with reduced computational cost

The sample dataset is generated by randomly sampling from the processed dataset while maintaining the same data format.

Note:
- The sample data is only intended for development and testing.
- Final model training and evaluation should use the complete processed dataset.
